 cut-off\nlatitudes is enhanced during epochs when the Earth's magnetic dipole is\nreduced, as already demonstrated earlier.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 21 Aug 2012 08:33:35 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-01-22"}
